le <a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-airpods-review-2021-160026883.html">在评测中给了 88</a>分，称赞定制驱动器和高动态范围放大器带来的宏大、身临其境的声音。内置的 H1 芯片让您可以使用免提 Siri 并与 iPhone 快速配对。尽管它们没有 ANC，但它们确实提供空间音频和自适应均衡器，可实时监控和调整声音。贴合舒适，这一代甚至还增加了防水功能，因此您可以带着它们在雨中跑步或散步。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p> Billy 的<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-wireless-earbuds-120058222.html">最佳无线耳机指南</a>中的几款耳机目前也在亚马逊上销售，其中包括<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAb7-mL3vWYbgxqntMrLAqdVwrhAfZHqycKDeZDAOlEDU&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FSennheiser-Bluetooth-Headphones-Cancellation-509180%2Fdp%2FB09T935X38" data-demonetize-referrer="https://www.amazon.com/Sennheiser-Bluetooth-Headphones-Cancellation-509180/dp/B09T935X38?th=1" class="rapid-with-clickid">Sennheiser 的 Momentum 3 耳机</a>。通常为 280 美元，46% 的大幅折扣使价格降至 150 美元。这些是总体最佳选择的亚军，并提供出色的声音和高端的聆听体验。它们没有我们<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9Tb255LVdGLTEwMDBYTTUtQmx1ZXRvb3RoLUNhbmNlbGluZy1IZWFkcGhvbmVzL2RwL0IwQzMzWFhTNTY_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tMXUwLTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiJkMzhhMmRhZi0yMDZlLTRiMzEtOTkyNC1jN2MyZGQxNjdkNzgifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAcvQb35Q0RnLk6l5bB41o5RKcfQvQDNTyNP4U-h_BCun&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FSony-WF-1000XM5-Bluetooth-Canceling-Headphones%2Fdp%2FB0C33XXS56" class="rapid-with-clickid">首选的</a>那么多功能，但现在也便宜近 150 美元。 </p><p><core-commerce id="3c2c48